data.description: This gorgeous stone home is a show stopper!  The home is nestled on a spacious lot and is the only residence on a dead end road.  If you want privacy this was is a must see.  The home is very spacious with over 3500 sq feet.  The house has all the key elements of a stone house:  thick wall, deep window sills, and endless charm.  The kitchen is good sized with ample storage and work space.  This living room is huge and will accommodate furniture of any size.  On the second story you will find 4 good sized bedrooms.  The property has a total of 3.5 baths so no need to share.  Don't wait call today for your tour.
